It will be sung simultaneously by all the performers in the three concerts.
The anthems will also meet at some point in a very unique live show on Czech television.
The lyrics of this song were written by Tomá<0xC5><0xA1> Hanák who also plays the main role of Jesus in the clip, Xindl X also sings...
How did you come to cooperate with them?
We collaborate with other personalities of the Czech show-biz, due to the fact that we organize many concerts and charitable events...
We strive to involve them intensively in these projects.
It turns out that most of them are interested in such cooperation and have fun.
What are the benefits of these concerts against the end of the world?
To equip the Studeo training center, which is accessible to people with reduced mobility and which we have been working on for the Jedli<0xC4><0x8D>ka Institute, with the association Tap, for six years.
