I confess, without a doubt, to be an amateur, and not a genius or an intellectual.
I try to find allies for my opinions and visions.
I've just gotten into politics and I'm trying to get the majority's support for my program.
I'm just trying to move things forward, and if it doesn't work, I'll stop in six years and go back to the private sector.
It's kind of like Okamura has to save the Czech Republic.
